<section
><title
>How to link to www.bibletime.info</title>
<para
> Please do not copy the images because they may change their design. </para>

<section
><title
>Larger banner</title>
<para
> Put the following HTML code on your pages: <programlisting>
<![CDATA[
 <a href="http://www.bibletime.info/" target="_blank">
 <img src="http://www.bibletime.info/images/banner/big.jpg" width="312" height="60" border="0"/>
 </a>
]]>
</programlisting
> This will look like this: <ulink url="http://www.bibletime.info/"
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
> <imagedata fileref="/images/banner/big.jpg" format="JPG"/> </imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </ulink
> </para>
</section>

<section
><title
>Smaller banner</title>
<para
> Put the following HTML code on your pages: <programlisting>
<![CDATA[
 <a href="http://www.bibletime.info/" target="_blank">
 <img src="http://www.bibletime.info/" width="88" height="31" border="0"/>
 </a>
]]>
</programlisting
> This will look like this: <ulink url="http://www.bibletime.info/"
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
> <imagedata fileref="/images/banner/small.jpg" format="JPG"/> </imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </ulink
> </para>
</section>


<section
><title
>Text link</title>
<para
> To insert a simple text link please use the following HTML code on your pages: <programlisting>
<![CDATA[
 <a href="http://www.bibletime.info/" TARGET="_blank">
 BibleTime - Bible study software for KDE
 </a>
]]>
</programlisting
> This will look like this: <ulink url="http://www.bibletime.info/"
>BibleTime - Bible study software for KDE</ulink
> </para>
